title: Let's Knit - April 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 26.4 Mb

Let's Knit is the UK's best knitting magazine! Every issue is packed with patterns for knitters of all ages and skill levels, with a fun and fashionable flavour that's perfect for today's knitter. It has all the practical help, informative features and shopping info you could possibly want, along with a fantastic high-value free gift with every issue
